OL,3,CBBC Radio 4 The Archers star Ian
OL,4,CPepperell dies following long illness
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to the actor
OL,7,FIan Pepperell, who was best known for
OL,8,Fplaying Roy Tucker in The Archers.
OL,10,FPepperell, who played the hotelier in
OL,11,Fthe long-running BBC Radio 4 drama for
OL,12,F22 years, died "in his prime" on
OL,13,FFriday at the age of 53 following a
OL,14,Flong illness, the BBC announced.
OL,16,FAs well as his radio role, he also
OL,17,Facted in numerous stage productions
OL,18,Fand briefly appeared in BBC soap opera
OL,19,FEastEnders.
